系统故障导致的，可全额退款；\n因不可抗力（如平台服务终止）导致电量无法使用的，按剩余电量比例退款。\n购买电量套餐后，未使用套餐内任何电量的，此套餐可全额退款。\n1.  **不可退款情形**：\n已使用的电量或因用户自身操作（如误删图片、主动消耗）导致的电量减少；\n用户主动充值后因个人原因（如不再使用平台服务）申请退款的；\n因用户违反本协议或平台规则被冻结账户的。\n1.  **退款流程**：符合退款条件的，用户可联系客服提交申请，平台将在 7 个工作日内核实并按原支付路径退还，退款金额以实际支付金额为基准，不包含优惠部分。\n### 五、用户与平台权利义务\n1.  **用户义务**：\n确保使用本人合法账户及支付渠道进行充值，对充值行为及后果负责；\n妥善保管账户信息，因账户被盗、密码泄露导致的电量损失，平台不承担责任；\n遵守本协议及《用户服务协议》《隐私政策》的其他约定。\n1.  **平台义务**：\n保障充值系统稳定运行，及时处理电量到账及异常问题；\n对用户的充值记录、账户信息予以保密（法律法规另有规定的除外）；\n1.  **免责条款**：\n因地震、网络攻击、支付渠道故障等不可抗力导致充值中断或延迟的，平台将尽力补救，但不承担额外赔偿责任；\n因用户设备故障、网络环境问题导致的充值失败，平台可协助排查，但不承担责任。\n### 六、其他条款\n1.  本协议与《用户服务协议》《隐私政策》具有同等效力，未尽事宜以相关协议为准。\n2.  平台有权根据业务调整修改本协议，修改后将在充值页面公示，公示 3 天后生效，继续使用充值服务视为同意修改后的条款。\n3.  因本协议引起的争议，双方应友好协商；协商不成的，可向平台所在地有管辖权的法院提起诉讼。\n4.  客服联系方式：通过平台 “帮助中心 - 联系我们” 提交咨询，或发送邮件至 system@tuggaigai.com。\n\n\xa9 2025 图改改 \xae 保留所有权利\n  ";return(0,i.rt)()||(e="\n# PhoText Compute Points Service Agreement\nWelcome to using the compute points service of PhoText (hereinafter referred to as \"the Platform\"). Before paying, please read this agreement carefully. Your recharge/subscribe behavior will be deemed as having read, understood, and agreed to all terms of this agreement.\n## Definitions and Explanations\n1.  **Compute Points**: A virtual service measurement unit provided by the Platform for users, which can only be used to offset image processing services on the Platform (including but not limited to editing text in images, removing text, adding watermarks, etc.). \n2.  **Recharge**: The act of users purchasing compute points through payment methods supported by the Platform. After successful pay, the compute points will be automatically credited to your Platform account.\n## Recharge Rules\n1.  **Pack Description**: Users can select the compute points packs displayed on the Platform (such as Basic Pack, Advanced Pack, Pro Pack, Single-Use Pack, etc.). The number of compute points included in each pack and the corresponding amount shall be subject to the real-time display on the recharge page. The Platform reserves the right to adjust pack contents and prices, which will take effect after being announced on the page.\n2.  **Payment and Crediting**:\n*   You must complete the payment through the payment channels provided by the Platform. After successful payment, the compute points will be credited to your account within 1 minute. In case of system delay, you may contact customer service for inquiry.\n*   If the payment is successful but the compute points are not credited due to network failures or payment channel issues, you can provide the payment order to contact customer service. The Platform will verify and replenish the corresponding compute points within 24 hours.\n## Compute Points Usage Rules\n1.  **Scope of Use**: Compute points can only be used to offset image processing services on the Platform. The number of compute points consumed by different services shall be subject to the prompts on the page during operation.\n2.  **Validity Period**: Compute points obtained through pay are permanently valid from the date they are credited to your account.\n## Refund Policy\n1.  **Refundable Scenarios**:\n*   If the payment is successful but the compute points are not credited, and it is verified by customer service to be caused by the Platform's system failure, a full refund will be provided.\n*   If compute points cannot be used due to force majeure (such as termination of the Platform's services), a refund will be made in proportion to the remaining compute points.\n*   If no compute points in the purchased plan have been used, the plan can be fully refunded.\n1.  **Non-Refundable Scenarios**:\n*   Compute points that have been used or reduced due to the user's own operations (such as accidental deletion of images, active consumption, etc.).\n*   Refund applications submitted by users due to personal reasons (such as no longer using the Platform's services) after active recharge/subscribe.\n*   Accounts frozen due to users' violation of this agreement or the Platform's rules.\n1.  **Refund Process**: For users who meet the refund conditions, you can contact customer service to submit an application. The Platform will verify and refund through the original payment channel within 7 working days. The refund amount is based on the actual payment amount, excluding the preferential portion.\n## Rights and Obligations of Users and the Platform\n1.  **User Obligations**:\n*   Ensure that you use your own legal account and payment channel for recharge/subscribe, and be responsible for the recharge/subscribe behavior and its consequences.\n*   Properly keep account information. The Platform shall not be liable for the loss of compute points caused by account theft or password leakage.\n*   Abide by this agreement and other provisions in the *Terms of Service* and *Privacy Policy*.\n1.  **Platform Obligations**:\n*   Ensure the stable operation of the recharge/subscribe system and promptly handle issues related to compute points crediting and abnormalities.\n*   Keep users' recharge/subscribe records and account information confidential (except as otherwise stipulated by laws and regulations).\n1.  **Disclaimer**:\n*   In case of recharge/subscribe interruption or delay caused by force majeure such as earthquakes, cyber attacks, or payment channel failures, the Platform will make every effort to remedy but shall not bear additional compensation liabilities.\n*   In case of recharge/subscribe failure caused by the user's equipment malfunction or network environment issues, the Platform can assist in troubleshooting but shall not be held liable.\n## Other Terms\n1.  This agreement has the same effect as the *Terms of Service* and *Privacy Policy*. For matters not covered herein, the relevant agreements shall prevail.\n2.  The Platform reserves the right to modify this agreement according to business adjustments. Modified terms will be announced on the recharge/subscribe page and take effect 3 days after the announcement. Continuing to use the recharge service will be deemed as consent to the modified terms.\n3.  Disputes arising from this agreement shall be resolved through friendly negotiation between the two parties. If negotiation fails, a lawsuit may be filed in the court with jurisdiction at the location of the Platform.\n4.  Customer service contact information: Submit an inquiry through \"Help - FAQ\" on the Platform, or send an email to system@tugaigai.com.\n\n\xa9 2025 All rights reserved, PhoText\xae\n    "),(0,n.jsx)(s.Z,{content:e})}},48805:function(e,t,a){"use strict";var n=a(57437),s=a(10566),i=a(8430),r=a(362),l=a(37238),o=a(52700),c=a(60268),d=a(59832),u=a(8350),m=a(91991),x=a(2265),p=a(43949),h=a(8633),f=a(94437),g=a(64654),v=a(11903),b=a(36760),w=a.n(b),j=a(42068),y=a(34766),N=a(15789),_=a(57154),k=a(40493),Z=a(65368),P=a(90031),S=a(83588),C=a(22201);t.Z=e=>{var t,a,b;let{className:I,onClose:E}=e,[M,{language:R}]=(0,p.$G)(),[z,T]=(0,x.useState)(0),[U]=(0,f.tS)([]),{enqueueSnackbar:A}=(0,g.Ds)();(0,s.d)();let[L,D]=(0,x.useState)(!1);(0,S.N4)();let O=_.r8||k.sT,q=(0,x.useMemo)(()=>O?null==U?void 0:U.prices_inr:(0,_.rt)()?null==U?void 0:U.prices:null==U?void 0:U.prices_en,[U,O]),W=O?"₹":M("pay.currency_symbol");return(0,x.useEffect)(()=>{N.default.validate();let e=setInterval(async()=>{N.default.validate()},5e3);return()=>{clearInterval(e)}},[]),(0,x.useEffect)(()=>{(null==q?void 0:q.length)&&(0,C.L)("view_pricing",{pricing_surface:P.t?"mobile_modal":"desktop_modal",pricing_currency:O?"INR":(0,_.rt)()?"CNY":"USD",pricing_plan_count:q.length,selected_plan_index:z})},[z,q,O]),(0,n.jsxs)("div",{className:w()("bg-white rounded-t-[18px] overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto max-h-[90vh] flex flex-col",I,{"flex flex-col":P.t}),children:[(0,n.jsxs)("div",{className:w()("h-16 overflow-hidden top-0 sticky z-10 shrink-0",{"shadow-lg":P.t}),children:[(0,n.jsx)("img",{src:"/img/pricing/tab-header-bg.png",className:"absolute left-0 top-0 w-full scale-y-125 -tr